//@version=6
// Probes (pine-lint --tv, 2026-06-25), UDF call sites:
//   f("hello") for f(int x)  -> CE10123 @ 5:7 (literal string / series int)
//   f(1, 2)    for f(int x)  -> CE10115 @ 5:8 (too many, passed 2 expected 1)
//   g(1)       for g(a, b)   -> CE10165 @ 5:6 (No value assigned to "b" ...)
// Clean: f(5), g(1,2), f(x=7), f() with a default.
indicator("s")
f(int x) =>
    x + 1
y = f("hello")
plot(y)
